          "type": "complete",
          "text": "Done. Commit a8e21885 pushed to jordanhubbard/nanolang main.\n\nUpgraded src/runtime/refcount_gc.h from RC-only (v1.0) to hybrid RC + Bacon-Rajan tri-color mark-sweep (v2.0). NLRCHeader extended to 12 bytes (refcount + size + gc_word with color/child_count/closure flag bits). Fast path: RC=0 → immediate reclamation. Cycle path: RC drops but >0 → add to purple suspect buffer; nl_gc_collect_cycles() runs MARK_GRAY / SCAN / COLLECT_WHITE. Triggered automatically on OOM before returning NULL. 19 tests passing (14 regression + 5 cycle tests including mutual-reference closure cycle)."
